author: Melody Schreiber, Susan Rinkunas, Kate Lowenstein
title: Interest in Home Births Is Spiking as Coronavirus Complicates Labor Plans
description: As hospitals limit support people and parents fear getting sick, home-birth workers say they're getting many more requests than normal.
content:
Kara is 39 and a half weeks pregnantand suddenly shes rethinking her entire birth plan.
 She always planned on delivering her baby at the hospital, as shed done with her previous two children. She loves her midwife, who collaborates with obstetricians at the… [+13637 chars]
